<P>
   Editors:
</P>
<P>
   The following is a recapitulation of stories concerning the OIC
report on Clinton. Where appropriate, writethrus are indicated.
</P>
<P>
   This advisory is being filed in `v' and `w' categories.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; QUESTIONS OR RERUNS: (888) 346-9867 &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; TECHNICAL PROBLEMS: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Peter Trigg
</P>
<P>
   Phone: (212) 499-3332.
