<P>
   Here are the stories that New York Times editors are planning
for the Page 1 of Monday, Sept. 14. The N.Y. Times News Service
supervisor is Tim Hilchey. The final FRONTPAGE will move later in
the evening.
</P>
<P>
   For copy info: (888) 346-9867.
</P>
