   For graphics, map, photo info: (888) 603-1036.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-DAY (Washington) _ Developments in the president's day.
By John M. Broder.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-JUDICIARY (Washington) _ A look at the Judiciary
Committee, one of the most partisan on Capitol Hill. By Lizette
Alvarez.
