<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHICS-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Sunday, 09/13/98. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been
posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON/Judiciary Committee -- 2X11 3/8 -- CLINTON-JUDICIARY
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON/Rebuttal -- 16pX6 3/8 -- CLINTON-RDP
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON/Sexual Encounters -- 2X2 1/2 -- CLINTON-RECONSTRUCT
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON/Texas, 17th District -- 1X4 3/8 -- CLINTON-TEXAS
</P>
